  "text": "Linking the holistic reflective analysis (stage 1) with the clusters of meaning (stage 2) led to the emergence of themes that appeared to be salient to a particular interview in terms of learning from failure. This process of clustering units of relevant meaning [CITATION_1] led to a 'master-theme list' for each transcript.",
