      "title": "Some guidelines for the phenomenological analysis of interview data‖",
      "abstract": "This article explicates, in a concrete, step-by-step manner, some procedures that can be followed in phenomenologically analyzing interview data. It also addresses a number of issues that are raised in relation to phenomenological research."
